metadata.name: Satosheena
metadata.description: Over the last few years, the blockchain devs have discovered undeniable evidence that Satoshi is real. In addition, they have identified 21 beings that claim to be his daughters. Found on different parts of the globe, these 21  beings, which are only partly human, claim to be the direct descendants of Satoshi himself. Their DNA is currently being examined. They claim they were sent to help with the development of the blockchain and to breed with humans to create a superior race.
